content:
Balanced sound. Noise isolation is adequate.

Build quality is pretty good. Sturdy cables - braided.

Fits comfortably in the ear, though you may want to use the duplicate eartips (the default one is a tad too large for me). Magnetic - so they can be secured around neck while not using.

If you're a metal-head like me, you might wanna look for something else as the bass experience on this one is somewhat lacking. But for vocals/pop/rock - this is an excellent choice! Recommended.
